{"article_id":"LALjeQ6iCMqfyffD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"There are `` no signs ''","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Edward Snowden worked with others ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"U.S. official says","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"The U.S. hacks computers in China ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"the NSA leaker tells a newspaper","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"He revealed secret U.S. programs","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"that collect data on phone and Internet activity","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"`` We have no information","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to offer , ''","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"a Chinese official says","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"China remained tight-lipped Thursday about its stance on NSA leaker Edward Snowden ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"who is believed to be holed up in a safe house somewhere in the semiautonomous territory of Hong Kong .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Snowden provided fresh fuel Wednesday for the controversy","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"he has sparked ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"telling a Hong Kong newspaper","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"that U.S. intelligence agents have been hacking networks around the world for years ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"including hundreds of computers in China .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"In the interview with the South China Morning Post , he also said","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"he plans to stay in Hong Kong","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"to fight any attempt","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"to force him to return to the United States","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"because he has `` faith in Hong Kong 's rule of law . ''","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"His comments come","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"as the FBI is investigating his case .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"His presence in the southern Chinese territory ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"which has a separate system of government from the mainland ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"has raised questions","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"about how an effort by the U.S. government","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"to extradite him","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"would unfold","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"and what role Beijing might play in the process .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"But China 's first official comment on the matter gave away no clues .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"JUST WATCHED Manhunt under way for NSA leaker","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"MUST WATCH Manhunt under way for NSA leaker","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"03:00","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"JUST WATCHED Ron Paul on Snowden :","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"It 's a heroic effort","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"MUST WATCH Ron Paul on Snowden :","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"It 's a heroic effort","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"01:54","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"JUST WATCHED Snowden 's life before leak","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"MUST WATCH Snowden 's life before leak 03:06","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"JUST WATCHED Obama open to NSA changes","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Obama open to NSA changes","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"02:31","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"`` We have no information","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"to offer at the moment , ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"a spokeswoman for the Chinese Foreign Ministry , Hua Chunying , said in response to a question about Snowden at a regular news briefing in Beijing on Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"She repeated the same answer to several follow-up questions .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Snowden , 29 , has rocked the Obama administration and U.S. intelligence community","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"by providing documents to journalists","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"revealing the existence of secret programs","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"to collect records of domestic telephone calls in the United States and the Internet activity of overseas residents .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"U.S. security officials homed in on Snowden","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"after Britain 's Guardian newspaper informed the Obama administration","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"that it was planning to publish articles","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"based on documents","depth":16},{"id":63,"text":"it had obtained ,","depth":16},{"id":64,"text":"a U.S. official said .","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"Authorities then quickly tried to determine who might have access to such information , as well as what documents were downloaded and by whom .","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"Snowden","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"-- who had taken leave from work at an NSA facility in Hawaii a few weeks before --","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"quickly came to their attention ,","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"said the official .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Authorities were `` making progress '' toward pinpointing the source of the leaks","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"when Snowden went public ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"said a second U.S. official .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"Both officials spoke to CNN on the condition","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"that they not be identified .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"There are `` no signs or indications ''","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"that Snowden had accomplices or tried to sell secrets ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"this official said .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Investigators think","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"the leaker is still in Hong Kong","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"and have a general sense","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"of where he is in that Asian metropolis .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"Snowden 's case has become a hot issue in that coastal city ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"making local newspaper front pages ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"stirring legal debates","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"and prompting plans for a rally in support of him over the weekend .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"The reaction in mainland China , on the other hand , has been muted .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"State-run media outlets have covered the case cautiously ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"appearing to try to avoid focusing too much attention on some of the sensitive issues","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"his disclosures have raised , such as government surveillance of citizens .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"The Snowden story has also so far failed to make big waves among China 's tens of millions of highly active social media users .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"Some Chinese state media took the opportunity Thursday","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"to highlight Snowden 's comments to the South China Morning Post","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"alleging","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"that the U.S. government has hacked Chinese targets .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"In recent years ,","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"the Global Times newspaper said in an editorial ,","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"`` the United States has always claimed itself to be a victim of Chinese hacking activities .","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"Many speculate","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"that it 's a cover up for hacking activities","depth":16},{"id":100,"text":"conducted by the U.S. government .","depth":16},{"id":101,"text":"Now , Snowden 's revelation proves","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"that such activities have already been going on for a long time . ''","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"Among some 61,000 reported targets of the National Security Agency ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Snowden told the Hong Kong newspaper ,","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"are hundreds of computers in China .","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"U.S. officials have increasingly accused China of being the source of thousands of attacks on U.S. military and commercial networks .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Beijing has denied such attacks .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"The South China Morning Post said","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"it had seen documents","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"provided by Snowden","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"but was unable to verify their authenticity .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"The newspaper also said","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"it was unable to independently verify allegations of U.S. hacking of networks in Hong Kong and mainland China since 2009 .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"Snowden told the paper","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"that some of the targets included the Chinese University of Hong Kong , public officials and students .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"The documents also `` point to hacking activity by the NSA against mainland targets , ''","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"it reported .","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"NSA leaker back in shadows","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"NSA leaker back in shadows","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"01:45","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Why did U.S. leaker hide in Hong Kong ?","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Why did U.S. leaker hide in Hong Kong ?","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"03:25 JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Where could NSA leaker go ?","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"Where could NSA leaker go ?","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"05:01 JUST WATCHED","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"Prosecution for journalists in leak ?","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"Prosecution for journalists in leak ?","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"02:46","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"The claims came","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"just days after U.S. President Barack Obama pressed Chinese President Xi Jinping to address cyberattacks","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"emanating from China","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"that Obama described as `` direct theft of United States property . ''","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"Snowden 's allegations appear to give weight to claims by some Chinese government officials","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"that the country has been a victim of similar hacking efforts","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"coming from the United States .","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"His claims came","depth":7},{"id":148,"text":"as Gen. Keith Alexander , the National Security Agency chief , testified at a U.S. Senate hearing","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"that the country 's cyberinfrastructure ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"including telephones and computer networks ,","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"is somewhat vulnerable to attack .","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"On a scale of one to 10 , `` our critical infrastructure 's preparedness","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"to withstand a destructive cyberattack","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"is about a three ,","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"based on my experience , ''","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"In the South China Morning Post interview","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"-- published one week after the Guardian revealed the first leaks","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"attributed to Snowden --","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"he said","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"the agency","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"he once worked for as a contractor","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"typically targets high-bandwidth data lines","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"that connect Internet nodes around the world .","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"`` We hack network backbones","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"-- like huge Internet routers , basically --","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"that give us access to the communications of hundreds of thousands of computers","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"without having to hack every single one , ''","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"the newspaper quoted him as saying .","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"A `` backbone '' is part of the inner workings of a computer network","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"that links different parts of that network .","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"It is used","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"to deliver data from one part of the network to another","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"and , as such , could expose data from multiple computers","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"if hacked .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"While refusing to comment specifically on a person under investigation ,","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"White House spokesman Jay Carney explained clearly","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"how and why U.S. authorities consider the leaks to be `` very serious . ''","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"`` They go right to the heart of our efforts","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"to combat terrorism ,","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"to combat efforts by extremists","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"who desire to attack the United States and the American people , ''","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"Carney told reporters Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"FBI Director Robert Mueller offered a similar assessment in testimony before Congress on Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"`` These disclosures have caused significant harm to our nation and to our safety , ''","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"Mueller said .","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"`` And we are taking all necessary steps","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"to hold the person responsible for these disclosures . ''","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"Snowden has n't been charged ,","depth":7},{"id":190,"text":"but he has told The Guardian","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"that he expects the United States to try to prosecute him .","depth":8},{"id":192,"text":"He worked for the computer consulting firm Booz Allen Hamilton until Monday ,","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"when he was fired","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"after outing himself as the leaker .","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"Snowden told the South China Morning Post","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"that he felt","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"U.S. officials were pressuring his family","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"and also accused them of `` trying to bully '' Hong Kong into extraditing him","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"to prevent the release of more damaging information .","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"He vowed to resist extradition efforts","depth":9},{"id":201,"text":"if it comes to that ,","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"he `` would rather stay","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"and fight the United States government in the courts ,","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"because I have faith in Hong Kong 's rule of law . '' `","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"` My intention is to ask the courts and people of Hong Kong to decide my fate , ''","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"the South China Morning Post quoted Snowden as saying .","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"`` I have been given no reason","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"to doubt your system . ''","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"But Hong Kong lawmaker Regina Ip , a former secretary of security for the territory , said Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":211,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":212,"text":"while any extradition process could take months ,","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"Snowden is n't necessarily beyond the reach of the United States .","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"`` If he thought","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"there was a legal vacuum in Hong Kong","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"which renders him safe from U.S. jurisdiction ,","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"that is unlikely to be the case , ''","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":219,"text":"Legal experts says","depth":8},{"id":220,"text":"that Beijing can get involved in the process","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"to extradite a person from Hong Kong","depth":10},{"id":222,"text":"if the case significantly affects defense or foreign affairs .","depth":9},{"id":223,"text":"But some observers say","depth":9},{"id":224,"text":"that Chinese authorities are unlikely to want to rock the boat in this instance .","depth":9},{"id":225,"text":"`` Given the somewhat fraught Hong Kong-Beijing relationship , the political impact of Beijing interference in this Hong Kong legal matter could be grave , ''","depth":9},{"id":226,"text":"the Beijing-based analyst and blogger , Bill Bishop , wrote in an article for USA Today .","depth":9},{"id":227,"text":"The newspaper said","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"Snowden has been hiding in undisclosed locations in Hong Kong","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"since checking out of his hotel room Monday ,","depth":11},{"id":230,"text":"a day after he revealed his identity in an interview with The Guardian .","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"Snowden told the Morning Post","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"he is not trying to evade U.S. authorities .","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"`` People","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"who think","depth":14},{"id":235,"text":"I made a mistake","depth":15},{"id":236,"text":"in picking Hong Kong as a location","depth":15},{"id":237,"text":"misunderstand my intentions , ''","depth":12},{"id":238,"text":"the newspaper quoted him as saying .","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"`` I am not here","depth":12},{"id":240,"text":"to hide from justice ;","depth":12},{"id":241,"text":"I am here","depth":12},{"id":242,"text":"to reveal criminality . ''","depth":12},{"id":243,"text":"The NSA and the national intelligence director did not immediately respond to a CNN request for comment .","depth":8},{"id":244,"text":"Asked during a media briefing Wednesday for comment on Snowden 's latest claims ,","depth":10},{"id":245,"text":"U.S. State Department spokeswoman Jennifer Psaki declined .","depth":10},{"id":246,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":247,"text":"she had not seen the latest South China Morning Post report .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":495,"left":0,"right":494,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":494,"left":301,"right":493,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":301,"left":254,"right":300,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":254,"left":250,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":249,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":251,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":278,"right":299,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":278,"left":270,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":263,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":256,"right":262,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":255,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":257,"right":261,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":258,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":15,"right":259,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":259,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":267,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":18,"right":266,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":266,"left